'''Aberni''' (yettwassenen s '''Lbaz''' ''الباز'') d [[aylal]] [[tisekliwin|asekliw]] yeṭṭafaren [[tawacult (tasnudert)|tawacult]] n [[iberniyen]], [[asallaf|adfar-is]] ɣezzif, [[asekkud|asekkud-is]] yuddes yettidir deg [[tagant|tẓegwa]], ytett seg [[tagemra|tgemriwin]] id iteṭṭef s tazla meqqren, 

'''Lbaz''' d awal [[Taɛrabt|Aserɣin]] (aɛrab) yettusexdem tikwal i weskan n [[aseflay|useflay]] maca aseflay d [[aylal]] yemgaraden yakk ɣef uberni acku [[aseflay]] yeṭṭafar [[tawacult (tasnudert)|tawacult]] n [[tiseflay|tseflay]] yerna aṭas n midden ur ssinen ara ula d isem-is 

== Talɣa n tfekka == 
Aberni ila (yesɛa) [[aqamum]] imesden d [[afriw|wafriwen]] ɣezzifen hrawen d imezgayen i wferfer, iṭarren-is uddsen (gedren) dgsen [[Akacbar|ikacbaren]] mesden Ayen id t-ittallen ad yeṭṭef tagemrawt-is akken ur t-reggel ara, [[Tawtemt]] n uberni tettili d asleg n ubleɣ n [[Awtem|uwtem]]

== Učči ==
Aberni d [[aɣersiw]] [[Timseksumin|amseksum]], yeggunin deg usekkud-is yuddsen deg tenzayt aṭas n telmas iy kecmen deg umuɣ n wučči ynes ama d [[Timsiffatin|timsuṭad]] meẓẓiyen neɣ d [[azrem|izerman]] d [[timraradin|temraradin]] n iden 

